data.description: Nestled in the scenic beauty of Floyd County, this three-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers a refreshing blend of country living and city convenience. Picture yourself sipping coffee on the covered deck, taking in the breathtaking views that stretch as far as the eye can see. It's like having your own private oasis! When it comes to location, this home hits the jackpot. It's a stone's throw away from Louisville, KY and the interstate, making commuting a breeze. You'll be living the best of both worlds—close to all the action, yet far enough to escape the hustle and bustle. Entertaining will be a delight, thanks to the generous 12 x 26 covered deck. Whether it's a barbecue with friends or a quiet evening under the stars, you'll have the perfect backdrop for creating lasting memories. This home is no stranger to upgrades. With a new roof, HVAC system, and flooring in 2019.  Need storage? We've got you covered. There's a large storage shed on the property, ready to house all your toys, tools, and treasures. Positioned on a hill, this home offers views that will leave you in awe. Experience the joy of waking up to the stunning countryside every day. You'll love the feeling of coming home to your private retreat, set back off the road. Don't let this opportunity slip through your fingers. Make your move today and call for a private showing.
